    "title": "Longitud de Arco",
    "content": "Para $y=f(x)$: $L = \\int_a^b \\sqrt{1+(\\frac{dy}{dx})^2} dx$. Para $x=f(y)$: $L = \\int_c^d \\sqrt{1+(\\frac{dx}{dy})^2} dy$.",
